'''豪華汽車'''，简称'''豪车'''，指的是裝備先進豪華、價格高昂的[[汽車|汽車]]，是[[經濟型車|經濟型車]]的相對。豪華汽車是一個市場化用語，汽車製造商會依據社會不同階層的購買力來製作不同水平的汽車<ref name=berger>{{cite book |last=Berger |first=Michael L. |title=The automobile in American history and culture: a reference guide |publisher=Greenwood |year=2001 |page=160 |isbn=978-0-313-24558-9 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=oRwMv8iNP-MC&pg=PA160&dq=%22a+group+of+car+marques+and+models+that+have+been+expensive+to+purchase |accessdate=2014-03-11 |archive-date=2014-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629125030/http://books.google.com/books?id=oRwMv8iNP-MC&pg=PA160&dq=%22a+group+of+car+marques+and+models+that+have+been+expensive+to+purchase |dead-url=no }}</ref>，衆多廠商之間對怎樣才算豪華或高價實際並無一定的標準<ref>Kapferer & Bastien, p. 43.</ref><ref>{{cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=YLuoXQ2NKmsC&pg=PA46&dq=We+know+that+luxury+is+relative+what+may+be+luxury+for+one+may+be+premium+for+another |page=46 |title=The Luxury Strategy: Break the Rules of Marketing to Build Luxury Brands |first=Jean-Noël |last=Kapferer |first2=Vincent |last2=Bastien |publisher=Kogan Page |year=2009 |isbn=9780749454777 |accessdate=2014-03-11 |archive-date=2014-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629125706/http://books.google.com/books?id=YLuoXQ2NKmsC&pg=PA46&dq=We+know+that+luxury+is+relative+what+may+be+luxury+for+one+may+be+premium+for+another |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，[[標準車|標準車]]、[[行政車|行政車]]、[[加長型禮車|加長型禮車]]和[[豪華旅行車|豪華旅行車]]等各種汽車也可算是豪華車的類別，某些汽車型號也會推出豪華特別版。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.theautochannel.com/news/2007/08/06/057385.html |title=The Original Luxury Minivan Adds Fresh Ideas for 2008 |publisher=The Auto Channel News |date=2007-08-06 |accessdate=2014-03-11 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612163403/https://www.theautochannel.com/news/2007/08/06/057385.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://www.forbes.com/2008/01/22/cars-minivan-luxury-forbeslife-cx_jm_0122cars.html |last=Mitchell |first=Jacqueline |title=Nine Minivans You'll Beg To Drive |journal=Forbes |date=2008-01-22 |accessdate=2014-03-11 |archive-date=2020-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200805235312/https://www.forbes.com/2008/01/22/cars-minivan-luxury-forbeslife-cx_jm_0122cars.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="consumer">{{cite web |title=Consumer Behaviour of Luxury Automobiles: A Comparative Study between Thai and UK Customers’ Perceptions |first=Jakrapan |last=Anurit |first2=Karin |last2=Newman |first3=Bal |last3=Chansarkar |url=http://economicswebinstitute.org/essays/carthai.pdf |publisher=Economics Web Institute |accessdate=2014-03-11 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030163725/http://www.economicswebinstitute.org/essays/carthai.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

